n Final Exam Strategy for Topic 2.2
1. Air composition percentages: memorise Nn=78.09, On=20.95, Ar=0.93, COn=0.042%.
2. PM classification: TSP > PMnn > PMn.n > PMn > UFP; finer = more dangerous.
