4. Chapman cycle: know all 4 steps; On+UV-C ® On; On+UV-B ® On (protective).
5. Ozone hole: CFCs ® Cl•; catalytic cycle; Montreal Protocol 1987; recovery by ~2060.
6. Smog: NOx+VOC+UV ® On+PAN; afternoon peak; VOC converts NO®NOn without consuming On.
7. London smog vs LA smog: reducing vs oxidising; SOn+fog vs NOx+VOC+sun.
8. Speciation: same element, different toxicity – Cr, As, Hg most important examples.
